@startuml
!theme plain
title Epic 28 - US115: Credits and Return to Menu
class CreditsController {
    + start_credits()
    + update_scroll(dt : float)
    + skip_to_menu()
    + on_credits_complete()
}
class CreditsState {
    + scroll_position : float
    + scroll_speed : float
    + update(dt : float)
}
class StateMachine {
    + change_state(StateID.CREDITS)
    + change_state(StateID.MAIN_MENU)
}
CreditsController --> CreditsState : manages
CreditsController --> StateMachine : transitions
@enduml